Real  Madrid  today said Cristiano Ronaldo has agreed to a contract extension with the nine-time
European soccer champion.  The 28-year-old Portugal international will attend a press
conference at the Santiago Bernabeu stadium later today, the
club said in a  statement  on its official website.  No details of the new contract were given.  Real Madrid this month agreed to pay 78 million pounds
($121 million) to buy Gareth Bale from Tottenham Hotspur.  Ronaldo and Bale both scored for Real Madrid yesterday in a
